quran[26]{c,v,t}:
  79,1,Ngwaalumbila (Achimalaika) ŵaakuchuŵaga (mitima ja makafili) mwamachili
  79,2,Ngwaalumbila soni (Achimalaika) ŵaakutyosyaga (mitima ja ŵandu ŵakulupilila) mwambolembole
  79,3,"Nguilumbila soni yaying'ambila mwangalechesya (munnengaleenga, mpela Achimalaika ni ndondwa)"
  79,4,Ni ŵaakutendesyana mpikisano (pakwanilisya malamusi ga Allah)
  79,5,Ni (Achimalaika) ŵaakuŵalaganya malamusi (ga Allah pakugaŵika m’mangwakwe)
  79,6,Lisiku lyalichigombedwa lipenga lyandanda (lyaliichitenganya chilichose ni kuwa)
  79,7,Lichilikuichisya lipenga lyaaŵili (yosope yene nikwimuka ni kola umi)
  79,8,Lyele lisikulyo mitima (jine) jichitetemela ni woga
  79,9,Meso ga (achinsyene) mitimajo gachiteteŵala
  79,10,"(Makafili) gakasatiji: “Ana uwwe yakuona chachituuchisya mukaŵe ketu kakala (nikuŵa niumi soni)"
  79,11,Kutendaga uwwe tuli maupa gepukuswe-pukuswe?”
  79,12,"Ŵatite (mwachisyawumi ni mwakuchindimbula): “Nakuŵaga kwele kuujilaako kusyene, basi kuchiŵa kuujila kwachasiko (kwangali ukoto kukwetu).”"
  79,13,Chisimu walakweo ni n'gumiilo umpepe
  79,14,Basi ajile sayi ŵanganyao tachigamba kuona ali pachanya petaka
  79,15,Ana jinyyiche abali ja Musa
  79,16,Pandema jaŵam'bilaasile Ambujegwe (Allah) pachiŵata chakutakata (chakuŵilanjikwa) Tuwaa
  79,17,"(Nikuntenda kuti): Jaawulani kwa Firiauna, chisimu jwalakwejo jusumbile mpika"
  79,18,"Ni nkajile: “Ana nkusaka kuti n'diiswejesye?”"
  79,19,“Ni nan'jongolele kwa Ambuje ŵenu kuti mwaajogopeje?”
  79,20,Basi niŵannosisye chisimosimo chekulungwa
  79,21,Nambo jwaakaaniile nikunyosya
  79,22,Kaneka jwachitundumalile (chikulupi) aku junankulimbichila (kwasiŵilila ŵandu kwa Allah)
  79,23,Basi jwaasonganganyisye (asaŵi) nikwaŵilanga (ŵandu)
  79,24,"Ni jwatite: “Une ni nam'mbuje gwenu jwapenani kusyene!”"
  79,25,Basi Allah ni ŵankwembekenye ni ipotesi ligongo lya maloŵe gakwe gambesi ni gandanda
  79,26,Chisimu mu yalakweyi mwana chaamuko kwa mundu jwaakun'jogopa (Allah)